1. The simple_form gem is making forms very easy to use in Rails. It is also able to deal with table associations. (See https://github.com/plataformatec/simple_form/)

2. Make sure the following gem is in the Gemfile
gem 'simple_form'

3. Execute the following commands
> bundle install
> rails g simple_form:install
> rake db:migrate
> rake db:seed
> rails server

